My hair's lovely and thick. Pity it's on my face: Mandy Appleyard's menopause diary
By
Mandy Appleyard
PUBLISHED:
20:37 EST, 10 November 2013
| UPDATED:
13:37 EST, 11 November 2013
66
shares
68
